Text: This is a hoax people ... save your time and bandwidth for something more important.  The compressed file is password protected and you have to sign up for all kinds of garbage with a promise that you will eventually get the password but each new link holds the same promise if you follow it ... you never get the password.
Uhm, it's not password protected. The file can be unrarred like you would normal do. No problems found with this torrent.
